snippet.title: GTFO Rundown 7.0 Rise Gameplay Trailer (4K)
snippet.description:
GTFO Rundown 7.0 now available on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/493520/GTFO/

GTFO is an extreme cooperative horror shooter where fighting for survival in a nightmare world throws you from gripping suspense to explosive action in a heartbeat. Teamwork is your only hope. Work together or die together.

Join the official GTFO Discord at: https://discord.gg/gtfo

Become an Ambassador at: http://www.gtfothegame.com

Follow us on:
Twitter @ https://twitter.com/gtfothegame
TikTok @ https://www.tiktok.com/@gtfothegame
Twitch @ https://www.twitch.tv/10chambers
And other social media with @GTFOtheGame

#gtfothegame 

About 10 Chambers:
Founded in 2015, 10 Chambers is a game studio based in Stockholm, Sweden. The studio was founded by Ulf Andersson, who founded Overkill Software and was the brain behind PAYDAY 1 & 2. GTFO is the debut title from the studio. More information about 10 Chambers is available at www.10chambers.com. For press and media inquiries, contact robin@10chambers.com.
